{"tid":569363,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)臨盆急先瘋 魔鬼末日","createTime":"2018-02-22T15:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T18:26:42.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70a6c54f0420fbbd18a0830e75040ab8775c2ff8","tid":569363,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7837789b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ee083502\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/53/Due_Date_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F53%2FDue_Date_Poster.jpg&h=9323fd90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/73/End_of_days_ver5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F7%2F73%2FEnd_of_days_ver5.jpg&h=7c828510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.彼得為趕回家中陪伴妻子產子，欲趕乘飛機回家，中途卻碰上了失意演員伊雲，二人被迫一同上路。可是，伊雲奇怪的性格卻令彼得深感煩厭，甚至引起多回爭執。正因為二人的性格南轅北轍，吵罵之間引出連番笑話，亦因著二人的化學作用，在公路上屢遇奇事，最後又化險為夷，甚至生出深厚友情．．．<br />\n<br />\n2.傑瑞柯是一名退休的警察，目前從事保全的工作。他和工作夥伴已經對工作感到厭倦。一次工作上槍擊的意外，慢慢牽引他走向一名年輕女子--克莉絲汀。克莉絲汀從小就經常在惡夢中見到一名男子，卻不知該名男子與自己的關係，直到一天，有一群神父闖進家門，意圖刺殺克莉絲汀，而傑瑞柯與夥伴即時搭救，她們才明白原來克莉絲汀是世界末日的關鍵......<br />\n<br />\n11 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9de63597\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nbInO7Y79mucol7PE8CahxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2bdf4f2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b523331484fce1c3b42f9394b68c4c662e8715","tid":569363,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bad643a7e75aa6246daa170fc4462aad8164ce9","tid":569363,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4c6bd76a4325a57c9b6a26a28ab5206502cc06","tid":569363,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695ef197c94ffb4921f8be1b972de87b71a0fff9","tid":569363,"uid":29160,"like"